title: Zulmi
subTitle: Raj is hired as a bodyguard for Komal, and the two grow closer to each other over time. However, things get complicated when he comes across Nihal, the man who molested his sister.

title: Gola Barood
subTitle: Shambhu, a criminal, saves Vijay's life and they become friends. When Shambhu's sister is kidnapped by a dreaded gangster, he is forced to loot a treasure.

title: Namak Halaal
subTitle: Arjun, a youngster, works at a hotel owned by Raja and serves him faithfully. However, when he learns about a plot to kill Raja, he decides to save him from harm at any cost.

title: Himmat
subTitle: When an Indian secret agent Abdul is killed in the line of duty, the mission is handed over to Ajay, his colleague and confidante, who decides to avenge his friend's death.

title: Dil Pardesi Ho Gaya
subTitle: After discovering that his brother is being held captive by the Pakistani army, Sunny takes on a false identity to rescue him. Trouble ensues when Sunny falls in love with a local girl.

title: Darr
subTitle: Swept up in a whirlwind of fear and romance, Kiran teeters on the edge of a mental and emotional precipice. While Sunil keeps holding on to her, Rahul spares no effort to drag her down with himself.

title: Beta
subTitle: After the death of his mother, Raju's father re-marries, but his stepmother is only after the family's money. When Raju eventually marries, his wife tries to make him realise what kind of woman his stepmother is.

title: Gumrah
subTitle: Seeing Roshni's talent for singing, Rahul gives her a break and they eventually fall in love. On a foreign trip, she is arrested for possession of cocaine, not knowing that it is all Rahul's doing.

title: Gumrah
subTitle: Seeing Roshni's talent for singing, Rahul gives her a break and they eventually fall in love. On a foreign trip, she is arrested for possession of cocaine, not knowing that it is all Rahul's doing.

title: Aatank
subTitle: Conflict ensues in a seaside town after two orphans stumble upon a trove of priceless pearls. The revelation leads to the discovery of a ferocious man-eating shark hunting in their vicinity.

title: Naina
subTitle: After years of blindness caused by an accident, Naina gets a successful cornea transplant. However, she soon begins to see terrifying visions that prompt her to investigate the source of her sight.

title: Deedar
subTitle: The marriage plans of Anand and Sapna are thwarted when it is revealed that Anand's business tycoon father had previously framed Sapna's father for a crime he did not commit.

title: Raja
subTitle: Raju and Madhu are forced apart by the latter's elder brothers, leading to increased distance between the two.

title: Dulhan Hum Le Jayenge
subTitle: Sapna is raised by her three uncles, each one of them with a contrasting pursuit in life. She falls in love with Raja, who tries to impress each of her uncles in a different manner.

title: Kya Kehna
subTitle: A young university student's world is rocked when her brief involvement with a wealthy playboy results in her pregnancy.

title: Vishwatma
subTitle: A policeman and a reformed criminal go to Kenya to comprehend a syndicate leader. However, they must break the rules of the land defended by Surya Pratap, a Kenyan police inspector.

title: Judwaa
subTitle: Twin brothers Raja and Prem Malhotra get separated at birth but are reunited by fate to defeat Ratanlal, a local gangster, who wants to destroy the Malhotra family.

title: Judwaa
subTitle: Twin brothers Raja and Prem Malhotra get separated at birth but are reunited by fate to defeat Ratanlal, a local gangster, who wants to destroy the Malhotra family.

title: Dil Se
subTitle: A journalist falls for an enigmatic woman who does not reciprocate his feelings. However, after he decides to marry another, the woman appears at his doorstep asking for help.

title: Panaah
subTitle: A gang of four blood-thirsty mercenaries are hired to hunt down a target named Raja. However, they experience a change of heart after the target melts their hearts with his innocence.

title: To Be Announced
subTitle: Bringing the best in television.

title: Apradhi
subTitle: After being framed by his own father for his mother's murder, Shiva becomes a contract killer on the condition that he not kill anyone with a family.

title: Ram Shastra
subTitle: Dhonga is sentenced to five years in prison after Ram Sinha busts his plans of assassinating the police commissioner. After his release, Dhonga seeks revenge on Ram who is now a police inspector.

title: Dil Ka Rishta
subTitle: Jai, a wealthy businessman in love with Tia, accidentally kills her husband in a car crash. After the accident Tia loses her memory and falls for Jai, who struggles with guilt.

title: Himmatwala
subTitle: After his sister gets killed on the day of her wedding, a man bumps into a woman who looks like his deceased sibling and resolves to help her with the love of her life.

title: Jeet
subTitle: Karan, a gangster, falls in love with Kajal, but she marries Raju because of her father's poor health. Later, when Raju finds out about his father's illegal business, Karan is hired to kill him.

title: Golmaal 3
subTitle: Cupid strikes when Pritam, a single father, comes across his college sweetheart, Geeta, in Goa. However, when their respective children go at war with each other, the two find it difficult to reunite.
